<br>
56-60th lvl characters have the option of forever surrendering their mortal shells and becoming immortal. All levelling would stop, but something similar to AAXP would be implemented (and hopefully in a better fashion) that grants immortal powers. The character is moved to the immortals server consisting of incredibly high level crap and possibly PvP enabled areas. I would also like to see something along the lines of a &quot;Lower Planes&quot; where the Immortals could move to, and then mortals from the other servers could come into a plane to challenge these Player Immortals. PvP and plane raids for the people who retained their mortality, and PvP for the immortals. The immortal would be seeded with a random loot drop, nothing would be taken from their inventory. Heck, a whole group of 6 immortals could come into Hate or Fear or something of the likes and have people come up to challenge them. To discourage immortals from playing dead to former guild members, they couldn't engage people from their original server.<br>
<br>
I will stop my rambling now.<br>
